                <div class="tit_nav">
                    <span class="tit_l">您所在位置：</span><a href="/Home/Index">首页</a><b>></b><span>案例信息</span>
                </div>
                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7230" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MKT-1122</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8315 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">央企如何服务地方：HY卫星科技“互联网+医疗”市场开拓与转型之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">How should central enterprises serve local development: The market development and transformation of HY Satellite Technology&#39;s Internet-based medical care market </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">郭功星，林泉，邹志波，赵佩华，蔡创能</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">汕头大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">庄贵军</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">广东航宇卫星科技有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">其他</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">12 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">HY卫星科技；市场开拓；航天科技；互联网+医疗；企业家精神</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">HY satellite technology; Market development; Aerospace technology; Internet-based medical care; Entrepreneurship</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">央企作为市场主体中的“国家队”，既要对接国家重大战略需求，落实国家重大发展战略，也要准确把握地方需要，服务地方发展，增进地方民生福祉。现有成果多关注于前者，而一定程度忽略了后者。本案例以广东HY卫星科技公司为研究对象，聚焦其在汕头经济特区的探索与发展，讲述其虽头顶“中国航天”光环，却一度落魄至“仅剩13名员工”，虽饱受风雨沧桑，却顽强不屈，凭借自身技术优势，精准把握当地市场需求，成功打开“互联网+医疗”市场，有效推动医疗行业“供给侧”改革，切实解决当地居民“看病难、看病贵”社会难题的发展历程。通过分析本案例，希望能够引导学员思考如何充分利用企业现有资源，精准发掘市场需求，找到企业转型发展之路。特别地，HY卫星科技的发展历程，也是时代发展的一个缩影，通过对本案例的学习，也应该引导学员在面临当前“百年未有之大变局”中，既要拥有大格局、大胸怀，也要关注小环境、小作为，见微知著，睹始知终，做到知行合一，于时代发展中有所作为。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">As the “national team” among market entities, central enterprises should not only dovetail with major national strategic needs and implement key national development strategies, but also accurately grasp local needs, serve local development, and contribute to local people&#39;s well-being. However, judging from existing studies, the former seems to have been prioritized, while ignoring the latter to some extent. Taking Guangdong HY Satellite Technology as the object of study, and focusing on its exploration and development in Shantou Special Economic Zone, this case study explored the company’s resilient journey from having “only 13 employees,” despite having the halo of “China Aerospace,” to achieving many goals, including: successfully opening up the Internet-based medical care market; effectively promoting the medical sector’s “supply-side” reforms; and earnestly solving the social problem of “difficult and costly to receive medical services” using its own technical advantages and by accurately grasping local market demand. Through this case analysis, the aim is to guide participants to think about how to fully utilize existing firm resources, accurately explore market demand, and find the road of corporate transformation and development. Notably, HY Satellite Technology’s development is also a microcosm of the development of the times. Hence, this case can also guide participants to not only look at the large picture and have a broad mind given the current “profound changes unseen in a century”, but also to pay attention to the small environment and deeds, be insightful, align practice with perception, and make a difference in the development of the times.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《市场营销》、《品牌管理》、《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业经营环境；危机应对策略；市场机会分析；细分市场选择；企业资源分析</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-03</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
